co.cask.tigon.sql.io
Class MethodInvoker

java.lang.Object
  co.cask.tigon.sql.io.MethodInvoker

public class MethodInvoker
extends Object

MethodInvoker This class is used for invoking the method of the callingObject. It uses POJOCreator to decode the incoming data record and instantiate an object of the method parameter type.
